text: Nizhnesapashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Yalchinsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 296 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 54 km from Mrakovo, 2 km from Yalchino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Nizhnesapashevo
